I meant what I said in there.

334
00:15:20.720 --> 00:15:23.560
Jamie. if I wanted to save myself.
I could have done it last night.

335
00:15:24.240 --> 00:15:28.560
And you would never have seen me again.
I would never have seen you again.

336
00:15:30.400 --> 00:15:33.000
