<i> Gonna kiss goodnight </i>

353
00:16:10.040 --> 00:16:11.680
<i>- And now I'll put up a fight... </i>
-[both moaning]

354
00:16:11.800 --> 00:16:13.720
<i>- ...But you won't say the words... </i>
-[Tina moans]

355
00:16:13.880 --> 00:16:15.680
<i> ...No. you won't say the words... </i>

