416
00:19:16.040 --> 00:19:18.560
Okay. I'm sorry. You're right.

417
00:19:19.560 --> 00:19:21.400
You've had my back 100 times
this year. girl.

418
00:19:21.520 --> 00:19:24.560
and I don't know how to repay you.
but I am trying.

419
00:19:25.880 --> 00:19:27.040
Thank you. okay?

420
00:19:27.800 --> 00:19:30.760
Look. I honestly haven't been
the same since Raina passed.

421
00:19:30.880 --> 00:19:33.040
Sometimes. I don't even know
who I am anymore.

422
00:19:33.960 --> 00:19:34.920
I know.

423
00:19:36.280 --> 00:19:38.080
I'm so sorry. Tash.

424
00:19:39.560 --> 00:19:40.600
[sniffles]

425
00:19:43.160 --> 00:19:45.000
S-- so you're not going to say anything?

426
00:19:45.840 --> 00:19:46.760
[scoffs]

427
00:19:48.120 --> 00:19:50.440
When have I ever said shit. Tasha?

428
00:19:51.520 --> 00:19:54.400
I've risked everything for your family
over and over again.

429
00:19:54.560 --> 00:19:56.360
and you still need me to prove my loyalty?

430
00:19:57.280 --> 00:19:59.520
Fuck that! What am I even being loyal to?

431
00:20:00.200 --> 00:20:03.200
-Some old purses that you gave me once?
-[scoffs] Wow.

432
00:20:03.720 --> 00:20:06.360
