and this isn't fair to either of us.

433
00:20:06.480 --> 00:20:08.320
You know what. you're right.
It's not fair.

434
00:20:09.040 --> 00:20:10.000
It's not.

435
00:20:10.880 --> 00:20:13.280
But just remember.
your name's on those papers. too.

436
00:20:14.000 --> 00:20:16.680
So if we go down... so do you.

437
00:20:18.160 --> 00:20:19.680
-Fuck you.
-Fuck me?

438
00:20:19.800 --> 00:20:22.280
This isn't friendship. This is blackmail.

439
00:20:23.280 --> 00:20:27.120
Look. I'm sorry about Raina.
but I loved her. too.

440
00:20:27.880 --> 00:20:29.560
