Oh. no. no. no.
Ghost and Tommy killed Lobos.

454
00:21:24.080 --> 00:21:25.840
And I don't know shit
about the second one. so.

455
00:21:25.960 --> 00:21:29.800
You don't have to know the details.
You just have to state that Alicia Jimenez

456
00:21:29.960 --> 00:21:32.600
took out Lobos because she wanted
to expand her territory.

457
00:21:32.720 --> 00:21:34.200
and then killed Mike
because he helped her do it

458
00:21:34.320 --> 00:21:35.400
and was a loose end.

459
00:21:35.720 --> 00:21:38.280
You sign the papers.
you go into protection immediately.

460
00:21:38.720 --> 00:21:40.600
New ID. relocation. the works.

461
00:21:41.560 --> 00:21:43.320
