That's why Mr. Hamilton is over there.
grinning like the Cheshire Cat.

960
00:46:51.800 --> 00:46:54.480
I object to the characterization
of my face. Your Honor.

961
00:46:54.680 --> 00:46:56.280
and I'm only here as an interested party.

962
00:46:56.440 --> 00:46:59.120
Well. what about it. Ms. Otombre?
Did your client tell Mr. Mak

963
00:46:59.240 --> 00:47:02.160
he heard about Sandoval's whereabouts
from AUSA Valdes or not?

964
00:47:02.280 --> 00:47:05.080
It wouldn't be the first time
a witness felt pressured

965
00:47:05.200 --> 00:47:07.360
by the DOJ to make a statement
under duress.

966
00:47:07.520 --> 00:47:09.000
-That's bullshit.
-Mr. Mak.

967
00:47:09.320 --> 00:47:12.720
Testifying for the prosecution
will harm my client's ability

968
00:47:12.840 --> 00:47:15.240
to continue his practice
in criminal law. Your Honor.

969
00:47:15.520 --> 00:47:19.320
What potential defendant will trust him
if he's working for the other side?

970
00:47:19.480 --> 00:47:21.040
I sympathize. I see your reasoning.

971
00:47:21.200 --> 00:47:23.000
-Your Honor--
-But. Mr. Silver

972
00:47:23.120 --> 00:47:24.320
is still an officer of the court.

973
00:47:24.600 --> 00:47:27.240
He has to appear and tell the truth.
no matter what.

974
00:47:27.440 --> 00:47:29.400
And where is your client right now.
Ms. Otombre?

975
00:47:29.560 --> 00:47:31.560
He should have been here half an hour ago.

976
00:47:36.240 --> 00:47:37.760
[objects thudding]

977
00:47:37.880 --> 00:47:40.360
What the fuck. John? You're leaving?

978
00:47:40.760 --> 00:47:44.000
Angela never pulled that recommendation
she gave me for the DC job.

979
00:47:44.400 --> 00:47:48.520
-I got it and I'm out of here.
-Come on. you can't bail on me now.

980
00:47:49.000 --> 00:47:50.640
leave me standing here
with my dick in my hand.

981
00:47:50.960 --> 00:47:53.120
I know we lost our leverage on Angela
with the Sandoval murder.

982
00:47:53.320 --> 00:47:56.440
but... we still got a witness
against Egan and St. Patrick.

983
00:47:56.680 --> 00:47:58.320
-Who?
-Maria Suarez.

984
00:47:59.480 --> 00:48:02.440
She called me today.
She-- she saw St. Patrick out in Queens.

985
00:48:02.600 --> 00:48:04.040
and she's pretty fucking worked up.

986
00:48:04.760 --> 00:48:07.040
And we-- we still have
Teresi's testimony on tape.

987
00:48:07.360 --> 00:48:10.040
Yeah. but Teresi's dead
and it's not gonna be admissible in court.

988
00:48:10.160 --> 00:48:12.000
Wha-- [sighs]
There are other ways to use it.

989
00:48:12.120 --> 00:48:15.320
We just-- we have to be creative.
Come on. look. I'm going to call Proctor.

990
00:48:15.760 --> 00:48:18.280
and then I'm gonna go for a ride
and stir shit up.

991
00:48:19.080 --> 00:48:20.640
-You in?
-Mm.

992
00:48:21.800 --> 00:48:22.920
I'm fucking out of here.

993
00:48:24.240 --> 00:48:25.680
This is bullshit. man.

994
00:48:26.200 --> 00:48:27.440
You're letting them win.

995
00:48:27.840 --> 00:48:29.560
<i></i>

996
00:48:30.760 --> 00:48:31.840
Good luck. Saxe.

997
00:48:40.120 --> 00:48:42.440
-[indistinct chatter on TV]
-[knock on door]

998
00:48:44.680 --> 00:48:46.880
-Who the fuck is that?
-I don't know.

999
00:48:50.440 --> 00:48:52.040
[door knocks]

1000
00:48:54.320 --> 00:48:55.840
Keisha. turn that shit off!

1001
00:48:57.240 --> 00:48:58.560
Go hide in the back.

1002
00:49:07.440 --> 00:49:08.360
Fuck you want?

1003
00:49:09.480 --> 00:49:10.640
<i></i>

1004
00:49:12.680 --> 00:49:16.720
Oh. I just wanted to extend my condolences
in person about your old man.

1005
00:49:17.280 --> 00:49:19.440
Too bad your former business partner.

1006
00:49:19.560 --> 00:49:22.600
St. Patrick and his girlfriend.
had your dad murdered.

1007
00:49:23.760 --> 00:49:27.160
-That's a lie.
-Angela knew Teresi was a snitch.

1008
00:49:27.640 --> 00:49:29.040
See. a guy in our office. John Mak.

1009
00:49:29.200 --> 00:49:31.240
told her in exchange
for getting a new job in D.C.

1010
00:49:31.520 --> 00:49:35.080
-God damn. you all are dirty.
-Sure. we color outside the lines.

1011
00:49:35.680 --> 00:49:39.120
But Angela knew. and you know
she shared it with St. Patrick.

1012
00:49:39.720 --> 00:49:41.680
That makes her the dirtiest of them all.

1013
00:49:42.120 --> 00:49:43.560
Teresi was a snitch.

1014
00:49:44.760 --> 00:49:47.080
He deserved to die.
no matter how it happened.

1015
00:49:48.320 --> 00:49:49.440
[Cooper] You sure about that?

1016
00:49:50.680 --> 00:49:53.920
Would it change anything
if you knew who he was snitching on?

1017
00:49:54.080 --> 00:49:56.200
-[recorder beeps]
<i>-[Teresi] Mike Sandoval?</i>

1018
00:49:57.040 --> 00:49:58.640
<i>Tommy didn't have nothing to do with it.</i>

1019
00:49:59.600 --> 00:50:01.520
<i>[breathing heavily] Because honestly...</i>

1020
00:50:02.560 --> 00:50:05.160
<i>Tommy's kept me at arm's length</i>
<i>about anything important.</i>

1021
00:50:05.520 --> 00:50:06.640
<i>I got nothing on him.</i>

1022
00:50:08.160 --> 00:50:12.560
<i>But I can give you St. Patrick.</i>
<i>Ghost... on a stake.</i>

1023
00:50:15.560 --> 00:50:19.160
If it were me. I'd seriously consider
flipping on Angela and Ghost.

1024
00:50:20.040 --> 00:50:21.640
I mean. they've certainly turned on you.

1025
00:50:23.400 --> 00:50:24.600
Your father loved you.

1026
00:50:25.680 --> 00:50:26.880
The tape proves it.

1027
00:50:33.120 --> 00:50:35.600
If you got people
expecting you somewhere...

1028
00:50:38.480 --> 00:50:39.760
I would go find them.

1029
00:50:40.360 --> 00:50:41.320
[scoffs]

1030
00:50:42.720 --> 00:50:43.840
I'll. uh...

1031
00:50:44.760 --> 00:50:45.840
fuck off.

1032
00:50:48.200 --> 00:50:49.600
Say hi to Lakeisha for me.

1033
00:50:53.720 --> 00:50:54.840
-[lock clicks]
-[recorder beeps]

1034
00:50:54.960 --> 00:50:58.160
<i>[Teresi] Mike Sandoval?</i>
<i>Tommy didn't have nothing to do with it.</i>

1035
00:50:58.520 --> 00:51:00.080
<i>[breathing heavily] Because honestly...</i>

1036
00:51:01.000 --> 00:51:03.560
<i>Tommy's kept me at arm's length</i>
<i>about anything important.</i>

1037
00:51:04.000 --> 00:51:05.840
<i>-I got nothing on him.</i>
-[recorder beeps]

1038
00:51:06.360 --> 00:51:09.560
<i>[Teresi] Mike Sandoval?</i>
<i>Tommy didn't have nothing to do with it.</i>

1039
00:51:10.120 --> 00:51:11.640
<i>[breathing heavily] Because honestly...</i>

1040
00:51:12.440 --> 00:51:15.040
<i>Tommy's kept me at arm's length</i>
<i>about anything important.</i>

1041
00:51:15.480 --> 00:51:16.640
<i>I got nothing on him.</i>

1042
00:51:17.000 --> 00:51:19.720
-You did it. right?
-[sobs]

1043
00:51:20.720 --> 00:51:21.680
Your dad.

1044
00:51:21.920 --> 00:51:24.160
<i></i>

1045
00:51:24.320 --> 00:51:26.640
That's why you said
you always hurt people that love you?

1046
00:51:31.760 --> 00:51:33.040
He told me...

1047
00:51:37.200 --> 00:51:38.400
before I did it.

1048
00:51:40.800 --> 00:51:42.520
He said he didn't snitch on me.

1049
00:51:44.200 --> 00:51:45.440
I didn't believe him.

1050
00:51:46.080 --> 00:51:47.000
You couldn't.

1051
00:51:49.160 --> 00:51:51.040
You understand why I did what I did?

1052
00:51:52.360 --> 00:51:53.360
Yeah.

1053
00:51:54.880 --> 00:51:57.720
And that's why we had to get away
from Ghost and Tasha. Tommy.

1054
00:51:58.800 --> 00:52:00.600
Ghost was supposed to be your family.

1055
00:52:00.800 --> 00:52:04.040
He could've come to me
if he knew about Teresi.

1056
00:52:04.520 --> 00:52:06.120
He didn't say a goddamn word.

1057
00:52:06.640 --> 00:52:09.520
And then. this morning.
when I told him that I did it...

1058
00:52:16.720 --> 00:52:17.800
I gotta go out.

1059
00:52:19.440 --> 00:52:20.360
I know.

1060
00:52:33.840 --> 00:52:34.840
Tommy.

1061
00:52:38.880 --> 00:52:40.400
I'll be here when you get back.

1062
00:53:09.600 --> 00:53:11.800
<i></i>

1063
00:53:14.960 --> 00:53:17.040
-[Angela] Tasha. come in.
-Thanks.

1064
00:53:17.560 --> 00:53:19.520
-Have a seat.
-[door locks]

1065
00:53:21.000 --> 00:53:22.080
Can I get you anything?

1066
00:53:22.280 --> 00:53:24.480
I'm having white
but I can open a bottle of red.

1067
00:53:24.640 --> 00:53:26.520
-No. white is fine.
-[Angela] Great.

1068
00:53:29.080 --> 00:53:30.000
[lock clicks]

1069
00:53:30.120 --> 00:53:32.080
Go ahead and throw your things anywhere.

1070
00:53:32.280 --> 00:53:33.840
-Mm-hmm. thanks.
-[cabinet door shuts]

1071
00:53:35.840 --> 00:53:37.800
Convincing Terry not to show up to testify

1072
00:53:37.920 --> 00:53:40.880
was a gamble and a much riskier plan
than having him perjure himself.

1073
00:53:42.440 --> 00:53:43.800
He must care about you a lot.

1074
00:53:44.440 --> 00:53:45.680
That wasn't my plan.

1075
00:53:47.440 --> 00:53:52.120
He was supposed to show.
I think that was your plan with Ghost.

1076
00:53:52.720 --> 00:53:53.880
Tasha. that's not true.

1077
00:53:54.200 --> 00:53:57.320
How else did Ghost know
that Silver was back? I only told you.

1078
00:53:57.720 --> 00:53:59.720
I haven't talked to Jamie
since this morning.

1079
00:53:59.840 --> 00:54:02.120
Maybe Silver left town again?
I didn't tell him.

1080
00:54:02.400 --> 00:54:03.800
-[Tasha scoffs]
-[Tommy] Oh. so you didn't tell Ghost

1081
00:54:03.960 --> 00:54:05.560
that Teresi was talking
to the feds. either?

1082
00:54:05.880 --> 00:54:07.480
-[door closes]
-[locks click]

1083
00:54:07.720 --> 00:54:11.720
Yes. that I told Jamie.
To protect you. to protect everyone.

1084
00:54:11.840 --> 00:54:13.200
I told Jamie to tell you about it.

1085
00:54:13.320 --> 00:54:15.360
-What's going on here?
-What do you think?

1086
00:54:16.240 --> 00:54:18.960
-[gasps] Whoa. hey. hey. hey.
-Well. Ghost didn't say shit to me.

1087
00:54:19.560 --> 00:54:24.400
He went to Vincent Ragni.
And Vincent had me kill Teresi.

1088
00:54:24.560 --> 00:54:25.560
<i></i>

1089
00:54:25.680 --> 00:54:29.000
Your buddy. "Ballsacks."
paid me a little visit.

1090
00:54:29.560 --> 00:54:30.760
He played me a tape...

1091
00:54:31.600 --> 00:54:34.560
where Teresi was talking about Ghost.
Didn't say shit about me.

1092
00:54:34.680 --> 00:54:36.280
And that's why you two broke team.

1093
00:54:36.400 --> 00:54:37.680
-No--
-To protect yourselves.

1094
00:54:37.800 --> 00:54:39.920
-That's not true!
-You don't know how long

1095
00:54:40.080 --> 00:54:41.320
I've been waiting for this.

1096
00:54:41.720 --> 00:54:44.840
-It's time for you to go. Angela.
-Wait. wait. wait. wait. wait.

1097
00:54:45.000 --> 00:54:47.440
How did Vincent prove to you
that Teresi was snitching?

1098
00:54:47.560 --> 00:54:49.360
Pictures. did he show you pictures?

1099
00:54:51.000 --> 00:54:52.600
Yeah. the pictures that you gave Ghost.

1100
00:54:52.720 --> 00:54:56.200
You need to get those back
because you can see Saxe's desk in them.

1101
00:54:56.400 --> 00:54:59.960
I'm the one who took those photos
of those pictures on his desk.

1102
00:55:00.120 --> 00:55:02.840
They'll trace back to me. then to you.

1103
00:55:03.440 --> 00:55:04.880
Saxe won't have any reason to believe

1104
00:55:05.040 --> 00:55:07.160
that Jamie would go
to the Italians with that information.

1105
00:55:10.000 --> 00:55:12.400
-[whimpers]
-No. Tommy.

1106
00:55:12.760 --> 00:55:14.040
I can't believe I'm saying this shit.

1107
00:55:14.360 --> 00:55:16.840
Go. Tommy.
We'll deal with this bitch later.

1108
00:55:17.040 --> 00:55:18.480
<i></i>

1109
00:55:18.720 --> 00:55:20.840
[Angela breathes deeply]

1110
00:55:21.000 --> 00:55:23.880
Tasha. I swear.
I didn't have Jamie kill Silver.

1111
00:55:24.680 --> 00:55:28.320
-If he broke team. he did that on his own.
-Would you be surprised if he did?

1112
00:55:29.040 --> 00:55:30.000
[scoffs]

1113
00:55:32.520 --> 00:55:35.600
-[door opens. closes]
-[exhales]

1114
00:55:37.200 --> 00:55:38.160
No.

1115
00:55:42.880 --> 00:55:43.920
[Vincent] Tommy.

1116
00:55:44.720 --> 00:55:46.320
I'm going to pour you
the biggest goddamn shot

1117
00:55:46.440 --> 00:55:47.680
you ever had in your life.

1118
00:55:48.440 --> 00:55:49.400
That's all right.

1119
00:55:51.520 --> 00:55:52.520
I can't stay.

1120
00:55:54.000 --> 00:55:55.120
Another time. then.

1121
00:56:00.040 --> 00:56:01.840
Look. I know I asked a lot of you.

1122
00:56:03.520 --> 00:56:05.000
But you did this family right.

1123
00:56:06.480 --> 00:56:09.080
So because of that.
whatever happened before...

1124
00:56:10.040 --> 00:56:11.680
is behind us.

1125
00:56:12.680 --> 00:56:13.760
Where'd you get 'em?

1126
00:56:15.480 --> 00:56:16.440
Huh?

1127
00:56:19.400 --> 00:56:21.160
Them pictures of Teresi talking.

1128
00:56:22.920 --> 00:56:23.880
Does it matter?

1129
00:56:25.400 --> 00:56:26.840
I killed my father for you...

1130
00:56:28.080 --> 00:56:29.240
for your family.

1131
00:56:31.560 --> 00:56:32.640
Tell me the truth.

1132
00:56:33.640 --> 00:56:35.480
<i></i>

1133
00:56:36.640 --> 00:56:38.920
Your friend. black guy in a suit.

1134
00:56:40.320 --> 00:56:44.000
He gave you those pictures.
so you would kill Teresi for ratting?

1135
00:56:44.160 --> 00:56:45.080
No.

1136
00:56:45.760 --> 00:56:47.280
He wanted you to do it.

1137
00:56:51.880 --> 00:56:52.800
[chuckles softly]

1138
00:56:56.120 --> 00:56:57.720
Let me get you those photos.

1139
00:56:58.520 --> 00:57:00.400
You got interesting taste in friends.
Tommy.

1140
00:57:00.600 --> 00:57:02.600
-[sighs]
-[Vincent] And I understand.

1141
00:57:03.160 --> 00:57:05.600
It's hard finding people
we can trust to go the hard way.

1142
00:57:05.800 --> 00:57:08.560
people who get it. get this life.

1143
00:57:09.520 --> 00:57:12.440
People who see in you
what no one else wants to see...

1144
00:57:16.160 --> 00:57:17.440
That we're monsters.

1145
00:57:25.400 --> 00:57:26.480
Anyway.

1146
00:57:27.120 --> 00:57:28.240
At least it's over.

1147
00:57:33.000 --> 00:57:34.040
Not yet.

1148
00:57:34.880 --> 00:57:36.240
One more thing I gotta do.

1149
00:57:38.640 --> 00:57:40.360
[Charles]
I don't have good news for you. Angela.

1150
00:57:42.360 --> 00:57:44.880
The case against James St. Patrick
may not be over.

1151
00:57:45.320 --> 00:57:47.480
A friend of mine was able to slip me
a witness statement

1152
00:57:47.600 --> 00:57:48.640
from a few weeks ago.

1153
00:57:49.720 --> 00:57:51.240
Jesus. I thought it was over.

1154
00:57:52.440 --> 00:57:53.840
I thought we'd won.

1155
00:57:54.240 --> 00:57:55.640
<i></i>

1156
00:57:57.240 --> 00:57:58.160
Who's the witness?

1157
00:57:58.680 --> 00:58:01.000
Have you ever heard the name Maria Suarez?

1158
00:58:02.040 --> 00:58:03.000
No.

1159
00:58:03.400 --> 00:58:05.920
Well. according to her statement.
Maria and her boyfriend. Miguel.

1160
00:58:06.080 --> 00:58:08.800
were kidnapped by Tommy Egan
and some of his guys.

1161
00:58:09.320 --> 00:58:12.160
They were taken to the basement
of the Truth nightclub...

1162
00:58:13.280 --> 00:58:16.040
where James St. Patrick.
who Tommy's guys called Ghost...

1163
00:58:17.240 --> 00:58:18.320
killed Miguel.

1164
00:58:21.640 --> 00:58:23.800
-Did Maria escape?
-[Charles] No.

1165
00:58:24.720 --> 00:58:26.120
She said Ghost let her go.

1166
00:58:28.640 --> 00:58:29.960
And there's something else.

1167
00:58:30.360 --> 00:58:32.080
You were right about. um...

1168
00:58:32.880 --> 00:58:35.560
Terry Silver. He is missing.

1169
00:58:37.560 --> 00:58:38.680
But how did you know?

1170
00:58:39.200 --> 00:58:40.760
<i></i>

1171
00:58:41.040 --> 00:58:42.400
[elevator bell dings]

1172
00:58:42.880 --> 00:58:43.920
James.

1173
00:58:45.600 --> 00:58:47.960
The case isn't over.
They have a witness against you.

1174
00:58:48.880 --> 00:58:51.520
And she is willing to testify.

1175
00:58:52.400 --> 00:58:54.920
You hear that? She. a woman.

1176
00:58:55.160 --> 00:58:59.600
A woman who could identify you as Ghost.
Now. who the hell could that be?

1177
00:59:03.840 --> 00:59:06.840
See. I know how Tasha felt
when you were inside.

1178
00:59:07.040 --> 00:59:08.680
She would not send you back there.

1179
00:59:09.320 --> 00:59:10.960
For the sake of the kids.

1180
00:59:13.560 --> 00:59:16.040
Look. listen.
there's only one explanation.

1181
00:59:16.160 --> 00:59:18.600
Okay. there's only--
there's only one woman left.

1182
00:59:18.720 --> 00:59:20.560
Now. you know I hate to be wrong.

1183
00:59:21.400 --> 00:59:24.240
But sometimes. I really hate to be right.

1184
00:59:24.880 --> 00:59:27.640
So. what are you gonna do about it. James?

1185
00:59:34.080 --> 00:59:35.080
Hey.

1186
00:59:35.320 --> 00:59:36.520
<i></i>

1187
00:59:36.680 --> 00:59:38.480
[Angela] Why did you want to meet here?

1188
00:59:40.640 --> 00:59:42.480
Just been thinking a lot. Angie. about...

1189
00:59:44.440 --> 00:59:46.560
how we got caught
making out in this stairwell...

1190
00:59:48.520 --> 00:59:51.720
about that last slice of pizza...
I took you to get

1191
00:59:51.840 --> 00:59:53.280
before you left for Choate...

1192
00:59:55.680 --> 00:59:58.280
About how long I've loved you.
I've always loved you.

1193
00:59:59.800 --> 01:00:02.000
Even when I hated you.
I still loved you. too.

1194
01:00:03.200 --> 01:00:05.040
I've always loved you. too. Jamie.

1195
01:00:10.080 --> 01:00:13.640
What did you mean today when you said
"I always save myself. and so do you"?

1196
01:00:14.000 --> 01:00:15.560
<i></i>

1197
01:00:15.800 --> 01:00:18.720
I meant that we both look out
for our own survival.

1198
01:00:20.960 --> 01:00:23.560
And sometimes that means that I hurt you.

1199
01:00:23.680 --> 01:00:24.640
[breathes sharply]

1200
01:00:24.760 --> 01:00:26.960
Sometimes that means you hurt me. too.

1201
01:00:28.840 --> 01:00:30.760
Proctor said the case
against me isn't over.

1202
01:00:32.400 --> 01:00:33.960
He said there's a witness against me.
Angie.

1203
01:00:34.080 --> 01:00:36.520
Said the witness is a woman.
Is that woman you. Angie?

1204
01:00:36.920 --> 01:00:39.080
Is that how you hurt me
for your own survival?

1205
01:00:40.200 --> 01:00:41.400
That's why you asked me here?

1206
01:00:41.560 --> 01:00:43.440
To figure out if I was testifying
against you?

1207
01:00:44.040 --> 01:00:45.040
Are you?

1208
01:00:46.920 --> 01:00:48.680
-No.
-Then who's the woman?

1209
01:00:51.400 --> 01:00:53.560
-[locker thuds]
-I thought we were supposed to be honest

1210
01:00:53.680 --> 01:00:55.000
-with each other.
-If we're being honest

1211
01:00:55.160 --> 01:00:56.560
with each other. Jamie.
what the hell happened

1212
01:00:56.680 --> 01:00:59.320
to Terry Silver. hmm? Did you kill him?

1213
01:01:01.400 --> 01:01:03.480
-You don't trust me.
-And you don't trust me.

1214
01:01:03.640 --> 01:01:05.440
Did you kill Terry Silver?

1215
01:01:13.600 --> 01:01:14.560
It's over.

1216
01:01:17.360 --> 01:01:20.320
If we can't be honest with each other.
there's nowhere we can go.

1217
01:01:21.920 --> 01:01:22.840
<i></i>

1218
01:01:22.960 --> 01:01:24.760
I know we said that we would
get back together

1219
01:01:24.880 --> 01:01:29.560
when this was over. but I think this. us.
needs to finally be done as well.

1220
01:01:31.720 --> 01:01:32.840
Good-bye. Jamie.

1221
01:01:34.200 --> 01:01:36.280
[cell phone ringing]

1222
01:01:41.840 --> 01:01:43.800
-[exhales]
-I didn't do it. Angie.

1223
01:01:44.000 --> 01:01:45.440
<i></i>

1224
01:01:53.920 --> 01:01:54.880
I didn't kill him.

1225
01:01:55.560 --> 01:01:56.720
I want to believe you.

1226
01:01:57.560 --> 01:01:58.520
So believe me.

1227
01:02:26.040 --> 01:02:27.400
[muffled grunting]

1228
01:02:30.240 --> 01:02:31.920
<i></i>

1229
01:02:57.240 --> 01:02:58.160
[gun cocks]

1230
01:02:59.720 --> 01:03:00.760
I love you. Angie.

1231
01:03:02.360 --> 01:03:03.640
-[gasps]
-[gunshot]

1232
01:03:03.800 --> 01:03:04.720
[gasps]

1233
01:03:05.800 --> 01:03:07.880
-[gasping]
-Jesus.

1234
01:03:08.120 --> 01:03:11.080
[gasps. whimpers]

1235
01:03:11.840 --> 01:03:13.520
[screams]

1236
01:03:13.640 --> 01:03:15.360
-[Angela] Jamie. Jamie.
-I'm here. shh.

1237
01:03:15.480 --> 01:03:17.960
-Jamie...
-I'm here. I'm here. [whimpers]

1238
01:03:18.080 --> 01:03:19.520
-[breathes heavily]
-[James] No. no. no.

1239
01:03:19.720 --> 01:03:22.280
<i>Angie? Angie!</i>
